msgid "2600:優愛が言葉を紡げば紡ぐほど、不自然さが際立っていく。[%p]"
msgstr "2600:Her words were sounding more and more unnatural as she talked.[%p]"

msgid "2700:僕を見ない。[linebreak]僕を見て笑おうとしない。[linebreak]さっきまで、あんなに穏やかに、あんなに優しく、話せていたのに。[%p]"
msgstr "2700:She wasn't looking at me. She wasn't looking at me and smiling. A moment ago, she'd been so peaceful, so kind.[%p]"

msgid "2800:僕は虚しくなってきて。[linebreak]もうなにも言わなくていい、って、心の中でつぶやいた。[%p]"
msgstr "2800:I felt so hollow and empty. “Please don't say another word,” I whispered in my heart.[%p]"

msgid "2900:[name]優愛[line]「み、見せてあげましょうか」[%p]"
msgstr "2900:[name]優愛[line]W-Want to see them?[%p]"

msgid "3000:優愛がカバンに手を伸ばし、くくりつけられたゲロカエルんを外そうとする。[%p]"
msgstr "3000:She reached out toward her bag and tried to take the straps off.[%p]"

msgid "3100:[name]優愛[line]「えーっと、ちょ、ちょっと、待って、くださいね……」[%p]"
msgstr "3100:[name]優愛[line]Um... j-just hang on.[%p]"

msgid "3200:その手が、少し震えている。[linebreak]焦っているのか、なかなかストラップはカバンから外れない。[%p]"
msgstr "3200:Her hand was shaking a little. Maybe she was nervous, because she couldn't get them off.[%p]"

