msgstr "3700:Room 36![%p]"

msgid "3800:『＠カフェ』で僕がいつも使っているＲＯＯＭ３７の隣室。先週、優愛に初めて会った日、いつもは空いているＲＯＯＭ３６に珍しく客がいて、『ニュージェネ』のまとめサイトを見ていた。[%p]"
msgstr "3800:The room next to room 37, the one I always used at @Café. The first day I'd met her, there had been someone in there, looking at a NewGen aggregator site.[%p]"

msgid "3900:そしてそのとき『＠カフェ』で僕は優愛を見かけて、[linebreak]慌てて店を出た――[%p]"
msgstr "3900:I'd seen her at the café, then panicked and rushed out.[%p]"

msgid "4000:まさか……[linebreak]あのとき、隣室にいたのは……[%p]"
msgstr "4000:Did that mean... the person in the next room over was...[%p]"

msgid "4100:僕は、ベンチに座って僕を見上げている彼女を見た。[linebreak]眼鏡の奥からこっちを見あげている視線とぶつかる。[linebreak]出会ってから、初めて目が合った。[%p]"
msgstr "4100:I looked down at her as she looked up at me. Her gaze from behind her glasses collided with mine. It was the first time our eyes had met since we'd known each other.[%p]"

msgid "4200:彼女はまだ微笑んでいる。でもすぐに戸惑いの色に変わる。[%p]"
msgstr "4200:She was still smiling, but it quickly turned into a look of uncertainty.[%p]"

msgid "4300:僕は、どんな顔をしてる？[linebreak]分からない。[%p]"
msgstr "4300:What kind of look was on my face? I couldn't tell.[%p]"

msgid "4400:視線を、彼女のカバンに――あのぬいぐるみストラップに――もう一度戻す。[%p]"
msgstr "4400:I looked back at her bag, and then the straps.[%p]"

msgid "4500:彼女が、ハッと息を呑む気配がした。[%p]"
msgstr "4500:I thought I heard her gasp.[%p]"

msgid "4600:[name]優愛[line]「西條……くん……？」[%p]"
msgstr "4600:[name]優愛[line]Nishijo?[%p]"

msgid "4700:さらさらと。[linebreak]黄色い葉が風に吹かれて枝から離れ、舞う。[%p]"
msgstr "4700:There was a gust of wind. Yellow leaves blew off the trees and danced in the air.[%p]"

msgid "4800:頭の中では、いろんな考えがグルグル回っている。[%p]"
msgstr "4800:A hundred thoughts were racing in my mind.[%p]"

msgid "4900:『ゲロカエルん』は、僕には理解できないけど流行ってるんだから、例え３つ同じ物をカバンにぶら下げている人間が何人もいたって珍しいことじゃない。[%p]"
msgstr "4900:Gero Froggy was popular, even if I couldn't understand why. There could be any number of people with three Gero Froggy straps on their bag.[%p]"

msgid "5000:だけど――[%p]"
msgstr "5000:But...[%p]"

msgid "5100:ＲＯＯＭ３６。[linebreak]あの日、優愛は隣に座っていたかもしれない。[linebreak]そしてそれを、これまで一言も言おうとしなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "5100:Room 36. Yua might've been sitting next to me then, but she'd never said a word about it.[%p]"

msgid "5200:そして『ニュージェネ』。[%p]"
msgstr "5200:And then there were the NewGen killings...[%p]"

msgid "5300:すっかり忘れかけていたけど。[linebreak]僕は、事件現場を目撃してる。[%p]"
msgstr "5300:I'd totally forgotten about them, but I'd been a witness to one of the crimes.[%p]"

msgid "5400:脳裏によみがえる、あのときの凄惨な光景。[linebreak]そして――[%p]"
