msgstr "5700:She gave me a slightly forced smile. Then she reached out toward her bag and tried to take the straps off.[%p]"

msgid "5800:[name]優愛[line]「最近、女子高生に大人気なんですよ。わ、わたしは、あんまりかわいいとは思わないんですけど……」[%p]"
msgstr "5800:[name]優愛[line]Teenage girls really love these things lately. I don't really... think they're that cute, though.[%p]"

msgid "5900:優愛の手が、少し震えている。[linebreak]焦っているのか、なかなかストラップはカバンから外れない。[%p]"
msgstr "5900:Her hands were shaking a little. Maybe she was nervous, because she couldn't get them off.[%p]"

msgid "6000:[name]優愛[line]「へ、変だな、どうして外れないんでしょう……っ。[linebreak]ちょ、ちょっと待ってくださいね、西條くんにも、見せてあげ――」[%p]"
msgstr "6000:[name]優愛[line]That's strange. Why won't they come off? Um... j-just hang on. I'll show them to you…[%p]"

msgid "6100:[name]優愛[line]「あっ……」[%p]"
msgstr "6100:[name]優愛[line]Oh...[%p]"

