msgstr "6800:If I looked at them closer, maybe I could remember. I wasn't sure what would happen if I did remember, but...[%p]"

msgid "6900:ただ、“分からない”っていうことの気持ち悪さから逃れたいためだけに、僕は――[%p]"
msgstr "6900:To escape from the awful feeling of not knowing, I...[%p]"

