msgstr "8700:It hadn't been zipped up, so her notebooks and textbooks went spilling everywhere.[%p]"

msgid "8800:[name]優愛[line]「あ、ああ、わたしったら、なにをやってるんでしょう……」[%p]"
msgstr "8800:[name]優愛[line]Oh dear... What am I doing?[%p]"

msgid "8900:ほんの数分前なら――[%p]"
msgstr "8900:Just a few minutes ago...[%p]"

msgid "9000:優愛のおっちょこちょいなところに、萌えていたかもしれない。[linebreak]でも今は、ただ凍り付くことしかできない。[linebreak]なぜなら――[%p]"
msgstr "9000:I would've thought the whole scene was very moe, but now all I could do was stare in shock, because...[%p]"

