msgstr "9100:By chance, one of the notebooks that fell to the ground had fallen open, and the small memos and newspaper clippings in it had scattered everywhere.[%p]"

msgid "9200:どうやらそれはスクラップブックらしくて。[linebreak]メモも、切り抜きも、すべて、ひとつの事件に関連しているものだった。[%p]"
msgstr "9200:It must've been some kind of scrapbook, because all the clippings and memos had to do with one subject.[%p]"

