msgstr "10000:[name]優愛[line]...[%p]"

msgid "10100:優愛はなにも答えなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "10100:She didn't answer me.[%p]"

msgid "10200:どうして、答えてくれないの？[linebreak]答えてよ……。[linebreak]なにか言ってよ……。[%p]"
msgstr "10200:Why won't you answer me? Come on... Say something![%p]"

msgid "10300:なにも言わないんじゃ、後ろめたい気持ちがあるんだって思っちゃうじゃないか……。[%p]"
msgstr "10300:If you don't answer, I'll think you're hiding something![%p]"

msgid "10400:せっかく、信じかけたのに……。[linebreak]優愛は、僕の味方になってくれるかもしれないって、[linebreak]思い始めてたのに……。[%p]"
msgstr "10400:And just when I was about to believe you. Just when I thought you were going to be on my side. Just when I was starting to believe that.[%p]"

