msgstr "10500:[name]星来[line]Don't believe anybody. Don't listen to anything anyone says.[%p]"

msgid "10600:やっぱり、星来が一番正しかった。[%p]"
msgstr "10600:Seira was right all along.[%p]"

msgid "10700:三次元の女は、どいつもこいつも最低なんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "10700:All 3D girls were garbage.[%p]"

msgid "10800:優愛だって、僕に好意なんてなくて、ただなにか目的があって近づいてきただけなんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "10800:Even Yua didn't like me. She was just trying to get close to me for some reason of her own.[%p]"

msgid "10900:僕を警察に突き出すつもりかもしれない。[linebreak]僕を脅すつもりかもしれない。[%p]"
msgstr "10900:Maybe she was going to turn me over to the police. Maybe she was going to threaten me.[%p]"

msgid "11000:最悪だ……。[linebreak]最悪だよ……っ！[%p]"
msgstr "11000:This was awful. Just awful...[%p]"

msgid "11100:あの事件のことはせっかく忘れかけてたのに。[%p]"
msgstr "11100:Just when I was so close to forgetting all about that murder.[%p]"

msgid "11200:警察もなにも言ってこないみたいだから、[linebreak]僕は無関係のままでいられるって思い込んでいたのに。[linebreak]巻き込まれたくなんてないのに。[%p]"
msgstr "11200:The cops had never come to say anything. I'd convinced myself that I'd never have to deal with it again. I didn't want to get involved.[%p]"

msgid "11300:優愛は、いったいなにが目的なんだ……。[linebreak]とにかく逃げ出したくて、僕はその場から踵を返そうとした。[%p]"
msgstr "11300:What was Yua after? I turned around so I could run.[%p]"

msgid "11400:でも――[%18]"
msgstr "11400:But...[%18]"

msgid "11500:手首を背後から優愛につかまれる。[%p]"
msgstr "11500:Yua grabbed my wrist from behind.[%p]"

msgid "11600:[name]優愛[line]「逃げるの？」[%p]"
msgstr "11600:[name]優愛[line]You're running?[%p]"

msgid "11700:その声に、ゾッとした。[%p]"
msgstr "11700:Her voice made me shudder.[%p]"

msgid "11800:背筋が凍りそうなほどの冷徹な声。[linebreak]さっきまでの優愛とは同一人物とは思えない。[%p]"
msgstr "11800:It was so cold I thought I might freeze. She didn't seem anything like the girl I'd been talking to a moment ago.[%p]"

msgid "11900:しかも――[%p]"
msgstr "11900:And...[%p]"

msgid "12000:[name]拓巳[line]「う……」[%p]"
msgstr "12000:[name]拓巳[line]Ugh...[%p]"

msgid "12100:僕の手首をつかんだ優愛の握力は、普通じゃなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "12100:She was gripping my wrist with incredible strength.[%p]"

msgid "12200:あまりにもきつく握りしめてきて、痛みが走る。骨まで握りつぶされるんじゃないかっていうくらいの激痛だった。[%p]"
msgstr "12200:She was holding it so tightly that it was physically painful. I thought for a moment that she might crush my bones, it hurt so bad.[%p]"

msgid "12300:振り払おうとしたけど、離してもらえない。[linebreak]それどころか、逆に引き寄せられ、僕は後ろ側につんのめった。[%p]"
msgstr "12300:I tried to shake her off, but she wouldn't let go. Instead, she pulled me closer, and I almost fell backwards.[%p]"

msgid "12400:[name]優愛[line]「逃げるの？」[%p]"
msgstr "12400:[name]優愛[line]You're running?[%p]"

msgid "12500:背後……しかも僕のすぐ耳元で、感情を押し殺したかのようなささやきが発せられる。[%p]"
msgstr "12500:She whispered in an emotionless voice, right behind me, and right into my ear.[%p]"

msgid "12600:ゾクリ、として、恐る恐る振り返る。[%p]"
msgstr "12600:I shivered, and slowly turned around.[%p]"

msgid "12700:[name]優愛[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "12700:[name]優愛[line]...[%p]"

msgid "12800:にらみつけてくるその瞳の奥に宿る色は、まともじゃなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "12800:The color in her eyes was insane.[%p]"

msgid "12900:[name]優愛[line]「逃がさないよ？」[%p]"
msgstr "12900:[name]優愛[line]I won't let you get away, you know.[%p]"

msgid "13000:[name]優愛[line]「騙してたことは謝るけど、お互い様だし」[%p]"
msgstr "13000:[name]優愛[line]I apologize for tricking you, but you weren't honest with me, either.[%p]"

msgid "13100:[name]優愛[line]「あなただって、隠してたこと、あるよね」[%p]"
msgstr "13100:[name]優愛[line]You were hiding something too, weren't you?[%p]"

msgid "13200:隠してた……こと……。[%p]"
msgstr "13200:Hiding... something?[%p]"

msgid "13300:そんなの、思い当たるのはひとつしかない。[linebreak]そして、どういうわけかこの女は、僕があの杭張り付け死体とその犯人を目撃したことを、知っていて。[%p]"
msgstr "13300:There was only one thing I could think of. Somehow, for some reason, she knew that I'd witnessed the crucified corpse and the killer.[%p]"

msgid "13400:そして、そのために僕に近づいてきたっていうこと。[%p]"
msgstr "13400:That's why she'd approached me.[%p]"

msgid "13500:やっぱり、この女は巧妙だ……。[linebreak]この女が僕に語った言葉は、全部ウソだったっていうことなんだ……！[%p]"
msgstr "13500:She really was a clever one. Everything she'd ever said to me was a lie![%p]"

msgid "13600:僕を一目見て存在が気になったっていうことも。[%p]"
msgstr "13600:That she'd gotten curious about me when she saw me for the first time.[%p]"

msgid "13700:ブラチューが好きって言ったことも。[linebreak]星来覚醒後バージョンのフィギュアを発売日に一緒に取りに行こうって約束したことも。[%p]"
msgstr "13700:That she liked Blood Tune... That she wanted to go buy the Seira Post-Awakening Version figure on the day it came out with me.[%p]"

msgid "13800:僕の話に楽しそうに相づちを打ったことも。[linebreak]僕ともっと仲良くなりたいって言ったことも。[%p]"
msgstr "13800:When she'd smiled at something I'd said... When she'd said she wanted to get to know me better...[%p]"

msgid "13900:学校に来ない僕を心配してたっていうことも。[linebreak]僕のことを偉いって言ってくれたことも。[%p]"
msgstr "13900:When she said she was worried that I didn't come to school... Even when she said I'd impressed her by coming to school...[%p]"

msgid "14000:全部全部、口から出任せだったんだ……。[%p]"
msgstr "14000:It was all lies.[%p]"

msgid "14100:悔しくて、悲しくて、僕はきつく拳を握りしめた。[%p]"
msgstr "14100:I clenched my fists in rage and anger.[%p]"

msgid "14200:くそぅ！\u3000くそぅ！\u3000くそぅ！[%p]"
msgstr "14200:Damn it! Damn it! Damn it![%p]"

msgid "14300:どうして僕は、こんな女の言うことを信じようとしたんだ……！[%p]"
msgstr "14300:Why was I ever willing to believe her?[%p]"

msgid "14400:[name]優愛[line]「本当は、もっと時間をかけて調べたかったんだけど、バレちゃったから、しょうがないよね」[%p]"
msgstr "14400:[name]優愛[line]I wanted to spend more time learning about you, but now that you've found me out, there's no sense in keeping up the facade.[%p]"

msgid "14500:[name]優愛[line]「あなたに、聞いてもらいたい話があるの」[%p]"
msgstr "14500:[name]優愛[line]There's a story I want you to hear.[%p]"

msgid "14600:[name]優愛[line]「聞いてくれるよね？」[%p]"
msgstr "14600:[name]優愛[line]You'll listen, right?[%p]"

msgid "14700:[name]優愛[line]「聞かないなんて言わないよね？」[%p]"
msgstr "14700:[name]優愛[line]You won't tell me you're not going to listen, right?[%p]"

msgid "14800:[name]優愛[line]「あなたは聞くべきよ」[%p]"
msgstr "14800:[name]優愛[line]You should listen.[%p]"

msgid "14900:[name]優愛[line]「聞いて」[%p]"
msgstr "14900:[name]優愛[line]I want you to listen.[%p]"

msgid "15000:[name]優愛[line]「聞くでしょ？」[%p]"
msgstr "15000:[name]優愛[line]You'll listen, won't you?[%p]"

msgid "15100:[name]優愛[line]「聞かないなら……」[%p]"
msgstr "15100:[name]優愛[line]If you won't listen...[%p]"

msgid "15200:[name]優愛[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "15200:[name]優愛[line]...[%p]"

msgid "15300:聞かないなら、なんだよ……。[%p]"
msgstr "15300:If I won't listen, then what?[%p]"

msgid "15400:今までの優愛とは別人みたいだった。[%p]"
msgstr "15400:She was like a totally different person now.[%p]"

msgid "15500:穏やかでおっとりした雰囲気は消えていた。[%p]"
msgstr "15500:That peaceful, easygoing manner she'd had was completely gone.[%p]"

msgid "15600:近寄りがたい雰囲気。そして異様なほどの執念を感じる。[%p]"
msgstr "15600:Now she looked cold and unapproachable, with a terrible intensity about her.[%p]"

msgid "15700:口調は冷静そのもの。いや、むしろ“冷徹”って言った方がいいかもしれない。[linebreak]いつもの弱々しさはどこにもない。[%p]"
msgstr "15700:Her words were cold as ice, as cold as death itself. The signs of weakness and helplessness she normally showed were nowhere to be found.[%p]"

msgid "15800:イヤだ、聞きたくない……。[linebreak]僕は耳を塞ごうとした。[%p]"
msgstr "15800:I didn't want to hear those words. I tried to close my ears.[%p]"

msgid "15900:でもできなかった。片手は優愛につかまれてしまっている。[%p]"
msgstr "15900:But I couldn't. She still had my wrist in her grasp.[%p]"

msgid "16000:さっきよりは握る力は弱まっているけど、なおも離そうとはしない。手を自由に動かせない。[%p]"
msgstr "16000:She wasn't gripping it as tightly as before, but she still wouldn't let go. I couldn't move my hand.[%p]"

msgid "16100:そのままの状態で、彼女はカバンの中から鈍色に光るなにかをおもむろに取り出し、僕の方へ差し出してきた。[%p]"
msgstr "16100:With her free hand, she reached into her bag and took out something metallic, and showed it to me.[%p]"

msgid "16200:[name]拓巳[line]「――――っ！」[%p]"
msgstr "16200:[name]拓巳[line]...![%p]"

msgid "16300:愕然となった。[%p]"
msgstr "16300:I gasped in shock.[%p]"

msgid "16400:心臓の鼓動が、一段階跳ね上がる。[%p]"
msgstr "16400:My heart felt like it was about to leap out of my chest.[%p]"

msgid "16500:冷静でいられない。[linebreak]ショックのあまり、耳を塞いでいた手を下ろしてしまっていた。その僕の耳に、優愛の残念そうな声が届いてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "16500:My mind began to race. I had my free hand over my ear, but I let it drop. And I heard her voice, sounding slightly disappointed.[%p]"

msgid "16600:[name]優愛[line]「この十字架に、見覚えあるよね？」[%p]"
msgstr "16600:[name]優愛[line]You recognize this cross, right?[%p]"

msgid "16700:もちろん、見覚えはある。[%p]"
msgstr "16700:Of course I did.[%p]"

msgid "16800:僕にはそれがなんなのか、すぐに理解できた。[%p]"
msgstr "16800:I knew exactly what it was.[%p]"

msgid "16900:それは十字架のように見えるけど、ホントは杭だ。[linebreak]こんな独特な形をした杭は、なかなか見ない。[%p]"
msgstr "16900:It looked like a cross, but it was actually a stake. Not many stakes had such an elaborate design.[%p]"

msgid "17000:少なくとも僕はこれまでに、一度しか見たことがない。[%p]"
msgstr "17000:At least, I'd only seen some once before.[%p]"

msgid "17100:――あの夜、路上に散らばっていた。[%p]"
msgstr "17100:That night, scattered on the road.[%p]"

msgid "17200:――あの夜、悪魔女が壁に打ち付けていた。[%p]"
msgstr "17200:That night, pounded by the demon woman into the wall.[%p]"

msgid "17300:――あの夜、死体を壁に張り付けにしていた。[%p]"
msgstr "17300:That night, pinning the corpse to the wall.[%p]"

msgid "17400:[name]優愛[line]「やっぱり、知ってるのね」[%p]"
msgstr "17400:[name]優愛[line]So, you do recognize it.[%p]"

msgid "17500:[name]優愛[line]「知ってるんでしょ？」[%p]"
msgstr "17500:[name]優愛[line]You recognize it, don't you?[%p]"

msgid "17600:[name]優愛[line]「知ってるに決まってる」[%p]"
msgstr "17600:[name]優愛[line]Of course you recognize it.[%p]"

msgid "17700:[name]優愛[line]「知らないなんて言わせない」[%p]"
msgstr "17700:[name]優愛[line]I won't let you say you don't recognize it.[%p]"

msgid "17800:[name]優愛[line]「知ってなくちゃおかしい」[%p]"
msgstr "17800:[name]優愛[line]You have to recognize it![%p]"

msgid "17900:[name]優愛[line]「知ってるよね？」[%p]"
msgstr "17900:[name]優愛[line]You recognize it, right?[%p]"

msgid "18000:[name]優愛[line]「しっ・て・る・よ・ね？」[%p]"
msgstr "18000:[name]優愛[line]YOU RECOGNIZE IT, RIGHT?[%p]"

msgid "18100:僕は必死で首を振った。[linebreak]イヤな脂汗が額に浮き出ていた。それを拭いながら、とにかく首を左右に振ることしかできなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "18100:I shook my head desperately. An awful sweat was forming on my brow. All I could do was try to wipe it off as I shook my head no.[%p]"

msgid "18200:[name]優愛[line]「これ、あなたの部屋にあったのよ」[%p]"
msgstr "18200:[name]優愛[line]This was in your room.[%p]"

msgid "18300:[name]拓巳[line]「……っ！」[%p]"
msgstr "18300:[name]拓巳[line]...![%p]"

msgid "18400:[name]優愛[line]「あなたの部屋」[%p]"
msgstr "18400:[name]優愛[line]In your room.[%p]"

msgid "18500:[name]優愛[line]「ベッドの下」[%p]"
msgstr "18500:[name]優愛[line]Under the bed.[%p]"

msgid "18600:[name]優愛[line]「床に落ちてた」[%p]"
msgstr "18600:[name]優愛[line]On the floor.[%p]"

msgid "18700:[name]優愛[line]「落ちてたの」[%p]"
msgstr "18700:[name]優愛[line]Lying there.[%p]"

msgid "18800:[name]優愛[line]「落としたよね？」[%p]"
msgstr "18800:[name]優愛[line]You dropped it there, didn't you?[%p]"

msgid "18900:[name]優愛[line]「それとも捨てた？」[%p]"
msgstr "18900:[name]優愛[line]Or did you throw it away?[%p]"

msgid "19000:[name]優愛[line]「とにかく落ちてた」[%p]"
msgstr "19000:[name]優愛[line]Either way, it was there.[%p]"

msgid "19100:[name]優愛[line]「落ちてたの」[%p]"
msgstr "19100:[name]優愛[line]Lying there.[%p]"

msgid "19200:この女……っ！[%p]"
msgstr "19200:When...[%p]"

msgid "19300:いつの間に、僕の部屋を調べたんだ！？[linebreak]初めて会ったあの日か！？[%p]"
msgstr "19300:When did she search my room? The day we first met?[%p]"

msgid "19400:僕が足をケガして、部屋まで送ってもらったときか！？[linebreak]星来のフィギュアを見て、かわいいと顔を輝かせていたあのときか！？[%p]"
msgstr "19400:When I hurt my leg and she walked me home? When she was staring with shining eyes and a cute face at the Seira figure?[%p]"

msgid "19500:[name]優愛[line]「この杭、外国製のすごく珍しい杭なのよ」[%p]"
msgstr "19500:[name]優愛[line]This stake isn't made in Japan. It's extremely rare.[%p]"

msgid "19600:[name]優愛[line]「それと……『ニュージェネ』第３の事件で使われた杭と同じ」[%p]"
msgstr "19600:[name]優愛[line]And it's just like the stakes used in the third NewGen killing.[%p]"

msgid "19700:[name]優愛[line]「同じなの」[%p]"
msgstr "19700:[name]優愛[line]It's the same.[%p]"

msgid "19800:[name]優愛[line]「同じよね？」[%p]"
msgstr "19800:[name]優愛[line]It's the same, right?[%p]"

msgid "19900:[name]優愛[line]「同じなのは間違いない」[%p]"
msgstr "19900:[name]優愛[line]I'm sure it's the same.[%p]"

msgid "20000:[name]優愛[line]「同じよ」[%p]"
msgstr "20000:[name]優愛[line]It's the exact same.[%p]"

msgid "20100:[name]優愛[line]「遺体を壁に張り付けにした杭と」[%p]"
msgstr "20100:[name]優愛[line]The same as the stakes that nailed the body to the wall.[%p]"

msgid "20200:[name]優愛[line]「同じ」[%p]"
msgstr "20200:[name]優愛[line]The same.[%p]"

msgid "20300:確信した。[%p]"
msgstr "20300:I was sure of it.[%p]"

msgid "20400:この女は、僕が『ニュージェネ』の犯人だと疑ってる。[linebreak]この僕を殺人鬼だと思い込んでいるんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "20400:This girl thought I was behind the NewGen killings. She thought I was the murderer.[%p]"

msgid "20500:探偵気取りか？[linebreak]『女子高生探偵・楠優愛』とか。[%p]"
msgstr "20500:Was she trying to be some kind of detective? “Yua Kusunoki, Teen Detective”?[%p]"

msgid "20600:死ね。氏ねじゃなくて死ね。[linebreak]アニメやゲームじゃ成立したかもしれないけど。[%p]"
msgstr "20600:You know what I thought? “Die, bitch.” I meant it, too. They weren't just empty words. I mean, this stuff might've worked in an anime or a video game.[%p]"

msgid "20700:優愛の推理は致命的に間違ってるんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "20700:But I knew that her theory had a fatal flaw.[%p]"

msgid "20800:僕は、犯人を知っている。[%p]"
msgstr "20800:I'd seen the killer.[%p]"

msgid "20900:この目で見た。[linebreak]あの悪魔を。[%p]"
msgstr "20900:I'd seen her with my own eyes, that demon.[%p]"

msgid "21000:名前の知らない女だった。[linebreak]でも翠明の制服を着てた。[linebreak]犯人は、僕の近くにいる。[%p]"
msgstr "21000:The girl whose name I didn't know... She wore a Suimei Uniform. She was close.[%p]"

msgid "21100:[name]拓巳[line]「だ……だから？」[%p]"
msgstr "21100:[name]拓巳[line]S-So... what?[%p]"

msgid "21200:[name]優愛[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "21200:[name]優愛[line]...[%p]"

msgid "21300:優愛はふとうなだれ、小さく息をついた。[linebreak]手首を握る力が弱まり、ようやく僕は解放される。[%p]"
msgstr "21300:She looked down and sighed softly. Her grip relaxed, and at last I was freed.[%p]"

msgid "21400:[name]優愛[line]「……それ以上でも、それ以下でもないです。ただ、あなたが知ってるかどうかを確かめたかっただけ。本当は、まだ言うつもりじゃなかったですし」[%p]"
msgstr "21400:[name]優愛[line]Nothing more and nothing less. I just wanted to see if you knew or not. I wasn't actually planning to ask you yet, anyway.[%p]"

msgid "21500:“まだ”ってどういう意味だ！？[%p]"
msgstr "21500:What did she mean by “yet”?![%p]"

msgid "21600:[name]優愛[line]「それじゃ、もうひとつ確認させてください」[%p]"
msgstr "21600:[name]優愛[line]Let me ask you one more thing.[%p]"

msgid "21700:[name]優愛[line]「あなたには、[color index="A0FF0000"]予知能力[color index="800000"]がありますか？」[%p]"
msgstr "21700:[name]優愛[line]Can you [color index="A0FF0000"]see the future[color index="800000"]?[%p]"

msgid "21800:[name]拓巳[line]「は……？」[%p]"
msgstr "21800:[name]拓巳[line]What?[%p]"

msgid "21900:思わずポカンとしてしまった。[%p]"
msgstr "21900:My jaw dropped.[%p]"

msgid "22000:予知能力、だって？[linebreak]なんだそれ？[linebreak]それが、事件となんの関係があるんだ？[%p]"
msgstr "22000:See the future? What the hell was she talking about? What did that have to do with the murder?[%p]"

msgid "22100:首をひねっていると、優愛はカバンの中に手を突っ込んで、画像がフルカラーで印刷された紙を引っ張り出してきた。[%p]"
msgstr "22100:I stood there, confused, as Yua reached into her bag and pulled out several full-color printouts.[%p]"

msgid "22200:[name]優愛[line]「予知能力があるって思わなきゃ、納得できないような画像データを、あなたが持っていたから」[%p]"
msgstr "22200:[name]優愛[line]If you can't see the future, then I don't know how to explain you having these images.[%p]"

msgid "22300:『将軍』が送りつけてきたグロ画像……！[linebreak]どうして優愛が持ってるんだ！[%p]"
msgstr "22300:The guro photos that Shogun sent me! Why did Yua have them?[%p]"

msgid "22400:[name]拓巳[line]「こ、これ……っ」[%p]"
msgstr "22400:[name]拓巳[line]T-These are...[%p]"

msgid "22500:[name]優愛[line]「あなたはどうして、『ニュージェネ』第３の事件の再現画像を持っているんですか？」[%p]"
msgstr "22500:[name]優愛[line]Why did you have a recreation of the third NewGen killing?[%p]"

msgid "22600:[name]優愛[line]「しかもこの画像が流出したのは、事件の前日です」[%p]"
msgstr "22600:[name]優愛[line]And these were from the day before the murder, too.[%p]"

msgid "22700:[name]優愛[line]「あなたの使ったＰＣに、キャッシュが残ってました」[%p]"
msgstr "22700:[name]優愛[line]They were in your computer's cache.[%p]"

msgid "22800:[name]拓巳[line]「ち、違う……っ！」[%p]"
msgstr "22800:[name]拓巳[line]N-No![%p]"

msgid "22900:これは、あの日初めてチャットした『将軍』とかいう男からもらったんだ！[linebreak]僕が作った画像じゃない！[%p]"
msgstr "22900:I got those photos from some guy named Shogun that I'd never even met before that day! I didn't make them![%p]"

msgid "23000:ダウンロードしたっていう履歴もちゃんと残ってるはずだ。そうだ、それを優愛に見せてやる！[%p]"
msgstr "23000:They should still be in my download history. I know! I could show that to Yua![%p]"

msgid "23100:っていうか、優愛はこの画像をどこで手に入れた……？[%p]"
msgstr "23100:Wait... where did she get these?[%p]"

msgid "23200:僕のパソコンにキャッシュが残ってたなんて、[linebreak]どうやって知ったんだ……。[%p]"
msgstr "23200:How did she know they were still... in my computer's cache?[%p]"

msgid "23300:優愛が僕の部屋に来たとき、少なくともＰＣを調べる時間なんてまったくなかったはずなのに……！[%p]"
msgstr "23300:When she came to my room, she wasn't there long enough to search my computer.[%p]"

msgid "23400:[name]拓巳[line]「まさか……君が……『将軍』か……！」[%p]"
msgstr "23400:[name]拓巳[line]Wait... are you Shogun?[%p]"

msgid "23500:僕をハメようとしてるのか！？[%p]"
msgstr "23500:Was she trying to set me up?![%p]"

msgid "23600:全部優愛が仕組んだことで、優愛も『ニュージェネ』の犯人のひとりで、警察の捜査を攪乱するために、僕っていうスケープゴートをでっち上げるつもりか！？[%p]"
msgstr "23600:Was Yua behind this whole thing? Was she one of the NewGen killers, trying to use me as a scapegoat to distract the police from the truth?[%p]"

msgid "23700:[name]拓巳[line]「た、助けて……」[%p]"
msgstr "23700:[name]拓巳[line]P-Please don't hurt me.[%p]"

msgid "23800:こんなの、あんまりだ……。[%p]"
msgstr "23800:This wasn't fair.[%p]"

msgid "23900:どうして僕なんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "23900:Why me?[%p]"

msgid "24000:僕がキモいから？[linebreak]僕に友達がいないから？[%p]"
msgstr "24000:Because I'm a creepy loser? Because I don't have any friends?[%p]"

msgid "24100:[name]優愛[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "24100:[name]優愛[line]...[%p]"

msgid "24200:優愛はなにも言わずに小さく首を振った。[%p]"
msgstr "24200:Yua just shook her head silently.[%p]"

msgid "24300:[name]優愛[line]「その画像は、『＠カフェ』ＲＯＯＭ３７のＰＣから拾ったんです」[%p]"
msgstr "24300:[name]優愛[line]I found these pictures on the PC in room 37 at @Café.[%p]"

msgid "24400:[name]優愛[line]「あなたのＰＣも、できれば調べたかったんですけど、その機会はさすがにありませんでした」[%p]"
msgstr "24400:[name]優愛[line]I wanted to search your computer, too, but I didn't have time.[%p]"

msgid "24500:ＲＯＯＭ３７……僕がいつも使っている部屋。[linebreak]この女、完全に探偵気取りか……。[%p]"
msgstr "24500:The room next to room 37, the one I always used at @Café... She really did think she was some kind of detective.[%p]"

msgid "24600:優愛は少しだけ申し訳なさそうな顔をして僕を見た。[linebreak]いつもの優愛に一瞬だけ戻ったような気がした。[%p]"
msgstr "24600:She looked just the slightest bit sorry as she stared at me. For just a single second, she looked like the old Yua.[%p]"

msgid "24700:その表情のまま、優愛はまたもカバンの中をあさり出した。[linebreak]今度は文字が印字されたプリントを取り出して、差し出してくる。[%p]"
msgstr "24700:She kept that expression on her face as she rustled through her bag again. This time, she took out a sheet with printed text on it and offered it to me.[%p]"

msgid "24800:嫌な予感がする。[linebreak]見ない方がいいって、理性が警告してる。[%p]"
msgstr "24800:I had an awful premonition. The logical part of my mind told me I shouldn't look.[%p]"

msgid "24900:でも、見ないワケにはいかない。[linebreak]抵抗しないと、濡れ衣を着せられちゃうんだから。[%p]"
msgstr "24900:But I had to. If I didn't find some way to resist, they'd pin it on me.[%p]"

msgid "25000:[name]優愛[line]「それが――」[%p]"
msgstr "25000:[name]優愛[line]That...[%p]"

msgid "25100:[name]優愛[line]「あなたのすべてです」[%p]"
msgstr "25100:[name]優愛[line]is everything you are.[%p]"

msgid "25200:僕のすべて？[linebreak]まさか、個人情報を完全に盗まれた？[linebreak]優愛ってハッカーなのか？[%p]"
msgstr "25200:Everything I was? Did she steal all my private information? Was she a hacker?[%p]"

msgid "25300:ドキドキしながら、僕はプリントを広げた。[linebreak]でも意外なことに、そこに印刷されていたのは僕の個人情報なんかじゃなくて、チャットの過去ログみたいだった。[%p]"
msgstr "25300:My heart pounded as I looked at the printout, but instead of my private information, it was just a chat log.[%p]"

msgid "25400:[name]拓巳[line]「あ……」[%p]"
msgstr "25400:[name]拓巳[line]Oh...[%p]"

msgid "25500:そのチャットの参加者は『ナイトハルト』と――[%p]"
msgstr "25500:It was a log of KnightHeart and...[%p]"

msgid "25600:『将軍』[%p]"
msgstr "25600:Shogun.[%p]"

msgid "25700:[name]優愛[line]「そのログ、変ですよね？」[%p]"
msgstr "25700:[name]優愛[line]There's something strange about that log, right?[%p]"

msgid "25800:[name]拓巳[line]「え……」[%p]"
msgstr "25800:[name]拓巳[line]Huh?[%p]"

msgid "25900:変って、なにが？[linebreak]普通のログだ。確かに僕は『将軍』とこういう会話を交わした覚えがある。[%p]"
msgstr "25900:What's strange? It was just a normal chat log. I remembered the conversation I had with Shogun.[%p]"

msgid "26000:[name]優愛[line]「『ナイトハルト』と『将軍』の――」[%p]"
msgstr "26000:[name]優愛[line]Look at how KnightHeart and Shogun talk.[%p]"

msgid "26100:[name]優愛[line]「発言時間が、全然噛み合ってないんです」[%p]"
msgstr "26100:[name]優愛[line]The timestamps don't match at all.[%p]"

msgid "26200:[name]拓巳[line]「あ……！」[%p]"
msgstr "26200:[name]拓巳[line]Huh![%p]"

msgid "26300:え？\u3000なんだこれ？[linebreak]なんで、こんなことに……？[%p]"
msgstr "26300:Huh? What was this? What was going on?[%p]"

msgid "26400:[name]優愛[line]「そこにある『ナイトハルト』は西條くん。発言時間は９月２８日の午前３時台」[%p]"
msgstr "26400:[name]優愛[line]The one labeled “KnightHeart” there is you. You're talking on September 28th, around 3:00 AM.[%p]"

msgid "26500:[name]優愛[line]「そして翌日、あなたは『＠カフェ』に行ってます」[%p]"
msgstr "26500:[name]優愛[line]And the next day, you went to @Café.[%p]"

msgid "26600:[name]優愛[line]「西條くんが『＠カフェ』に行くのは、学校帰りと決まってる」[%p]"
msgstr "26600:[name]優愛[line]You always go to @Café after you leave school.[%p]"

msgid "26700:[name]優愛[line]「そして学校に行くのは、週に２．５回。あなたのクラスメイトから聞いたんですけど、先週あなたが学校に来た日は――」[%p]"
msgstr "26700:[name]優愛[line]And you go to school roughly 2.5 times per week. I asked one of your classmates, and they said the days you went to school last week were...[%p]"

msgid "26800:[name]優愛[line]「月曜日、水曜日、木曜日」[%p]"
msgstr "26800:[name]優愛[line]Monday, Wednesday, and Thursday.[%p]"

msgid "26900:[name]優愛[line]「先週の月曜日は……９月２９日。『将軍』の発言時間と同じ日です」[%p]"
msgstr "26900:[name]優愛[line]The Monday of last week was September 29th, the same day Shogun was in the chat.[%p]"

msgid "27000:[name]拓巳[line]「…………な……」[%p]"
msgstr "27000:[name]拓巳[line]What?[%p]"

msgid "27100:なんだ？\u3000なにを……言ってるんだ……？[%p]"
msgstr "27100:What? What was she talking about?[%p]"

msgid "27200:[name]優愛[line]「ＲＯＯＭ３７のＰＣのチャットログを調べさせてもらいました」[%p]"
msgstr "27200:[name]優愛[line]I looked at the chat log for the PC in room 37, too.[%p]"

msgid "27300:[name]優愛[line]「そこから分かったことは……」[%p]"
msgstr "27300:[name]優愛[line]And what I learned was...[%p]"

msgid "27400:優愛は少しだけ、言葉を切り――[%p]"
msgstr "27400:She paused for just a moment,[%p]"

msgid "27500:やがて視線をまっすぐに僕へと見据え、残酷な事実を口にした。[%p]"
msgstr "27500:before looking right at me and delivering a cruel truth.[%p]"

msgid "27600:[name]優愛[line]「あなたひとりの自作自演……」[%p]"
msgstr "27600:[name]優愛[line]This whole thing was an act you put on.[%p]"

msgid "27700:[margin top="266"][center]――僕を、見るな。[unk19 index="30"]"
msgstr "27700:[margin top="266"][center]—Don't look at me.[unk19 index="30"]"

msgid "27800:[name]優愛[line]「『将軍』は――」[%p]"
msgstr "27800:[name]優愛[line]Shogun is...[%p]"

msgid "27900:[margin top="266"][center]――僕を、見るな！[unk19 index="30"]"
msgstr "27900:[margin top="266"][center]—Don't look at me![unk19 index="30"]"

msgid "28000:[name]優愛[line]「あなた自身」[%p]"
msgstr "28000:[name]優愛[line]... you.[%p]"

